RoboActionPainting series by Dragan Ilić...

RoboActionPainting series by Dragan Ilić features abstracted mark-making using an industrial robot, sometimes carrying and guiding the artist himself: The artist constantly transposes into the third dimension his decade's long-running conceptual practice based on the usage of pencils as the basic draftsman's tool, starting primarily with the media of performance art, installation and sculpture in extended field.
